title: 2013 Release of Blitzkrieg Complete Anthology
description:
This Blitzkrieg Complete anthology was released November 19, 2013 and is the first time that the Blitzkrieg series has been optimized for windows vista, 7 and 8 ..

Here's a link where you can read about it, and where it was bought.




 ----It contains the following---

 1. Blitzkrieg 1
 
 2. Burning Horizon

 3. Rolling Thunder

 4. Blitzkrieg 2

 5. Fall of the Reich

 6. Liberation  

 and more.....
